summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over a portion of the northeast one-quarter of Section 10, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; a portion of Government Lots 4 and 5 in Section 11, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and the First Class Shore Lands adjoining said Government Lot 5; a portion the southeast one quarter of Section 10, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; a portion of Block "A" of the unrecorded plat of Windermere in Section 10; Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M; a portion of Block 2, Hawthorne Heights No. 6 for storm drain purposes; ALSO, a portion of Block C. Windermere, a Replat of a portion of Montlake Tracts for sanitary sewer and storm drain purposes. (Lake Washington Northeast, Contract 3, Sewer Improvement Project)
